{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2439770/extras/ValenciaRain2.gif?t=1737248519\" /><strong>Project Mix</strong> is a VR anime cyberpunk bartending narrative game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play as Rone, a former thug who starts a new life as a bartender in the seedy red light district of Nirvana. At first, you live by the paycheck working at Eleventh Heaven, but as you find yourself hearing a bit too much for your own good, you find yourself thrown into a deep conspiracy. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">If you love games like VA-11 Hall-A, Yakuza, and the Persona series, you don't want to miss this out! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Key Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Deepen relationships with 6 unique clients and potentially develop a romance with them.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2439770/extras/KatieGif.gif?t=1737248519\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> What you choose to serve changes the lives of your clients, and even the game narrative.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2439770/extras/BeerServing_December_2023.gif?t=1737248519\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore the world through gorgeous and atmospheric environments featuring stylized anime visuals.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2439770/extras/environmentsshowcase.gif?t=1737248519\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Shake, pour, decorate, and serve. Interactive bartending mechanics built from the ground up for VR.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2439770/extras/DrinksGif.gif?t=1737248519\" /></p></l